{"tid":1047273,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[簡介/多圖] 巴西 里約嘉年華2019","createTime":"2019-03-05T00:14:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-06T02:41:26.000Z","uid":231598,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"413355f59d493cd9afb48f88ffe5dcf96e099792","tid":1047273,"uid":231598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T00:14:46.000Z","msg":"除左世界盃同足球<br />\n講起巴西應該都會諗起森巴女郎<br />\n<br />\n咁啱小弟前幾日就去左里約睇<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">森巴嘉年華</span><br />\n又知道網上中文嘅資料都唔係太多<br />\n所以就想趁呢個機會同大家分享下<br />\n（有咩錯嘅資料，歡迎糾正）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首先，講下張<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">機票</span></span><br />\n因為我黎南美玩兩個幾月<br />\n實際幾時走，去邊都未confirm<br />\n所以我係買單程由香港飛巴西聖保羅<br />\n再由聖保羅轉內陸機黎里約熱內盧<br />\n<br />\n香港係冇直航飛去巴西<br />\n所以其實點都要起碼30個鐘先黎到<br />\n我張單程香港飛聖保羅係3800hkd<br />\n分開買嗰張聖保羅去里約嗰張就500hkd<br />\n加埋<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">4300</span><br />\n<br />\n上網睇過<br />\n直接買香港來回里約嘅話都成10000蚊<br />\n而來回聖保羅就7000<br />\n加埋程來回內陸機一千有找<br />\n總共就~<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">8000</span><br />\n咁就慳到兩千蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">記住，聖保羅有兩個機場<br />\n留意自己喺邊度落機先好買嗰程內陸機</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後就講下<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">咩係嘉年華？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n嘉年華喺巴西係一個好重要嘅節日，每逢到左呢個時候，街上就會有好多人出黎唱歌跳舞，慶祝一番。<br />\n<br />\n其實巴西有好多地方都有嘉年華，但最轟動嘅應該就係里約森巴嘉年華，其實有啲似花車巡遊。一連幾日嘅比賽會喺森巴舞劇場舉行，黎自巴西唔同地方嘅Samba schools都會黎參賽，鬥過你死我活。<br />\n<br />\n有關嘉年華嗰啲歷史、由來我唔多講喇，上網都易搵到。<br />\n最主要想講多啲practical嘅野。"},{"pid":"dec4db12457f9077e22d9217d85b43b11a171783","tid":1047273,"uid":231598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T00:15:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">幾時係嘉年華？</span></span><br />\n復活節前50日至前40日就係狂歡節，因為復活節前40日係都係齋戒日，所以佢地齋戒之前就要狂歡一番。<br />\n至於森巴嘉年華，係分五日進行，由嗰十日𥚃面嘅第一個星期五，一連四日。另外決賽表演就會喺第二個星期六進行。<br />\n<br />\n即係今年復活節係4月21日<br />\n50日之前就係3月1<br />\n3月1係星期五，所以比賽會係3月1-5日<br />\n另外決賽表演就會係3月9日<br />\n（時間係9pm-4,5am）<br />\n<br />\n咁幾時係復活節？呢個問題太深，答你唔到。<br />\n<br />\n都係直接上網睇下幾時係嘉年華好過啦。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">咁多日有咩分別？睇邊日好？</span></span><br />\n簡單講<br />\n頭兩日(3月1,2)係初級組，Access group<br />\n後兩日(3月3,4)係高級組，Special group<br />\n後兩日比賽嘅十幾隊，就會排名1-6<br />\n喺第二個星期六再表演。<br />\n<br />\n由於勝負已分，所以3月9日氣氛都冇高級組比賽嗰兩日咁好。<br />\n<br />\n不過唔同日子嘅價錢都會差好遠，自己揀啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/04/112606_3cb7972baa647718c53dc5a48bae173d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F04%2F112606_3cb7972baa647718c53dc5a48bae173d.png&h=96211650&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">係咪真係一票難求？點買飛？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n一年一度嘅盛事，世界各地嘅遊客都湧去睇<br />\n應該都好難買飛架啦<br />\n<br />\n我初頭都係咁諗<br />\n<br />\n不過原來真係好睇你邊場，坐咩位<br />\n<br />\n我睇第一場，我喺比賽嘅前一兩日都仲買到飛<br />\n<br />\n其實啲飛嘅價錢可以好大差別，平至40蚊美金，貴至幾百蚊美金。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/04/112638_11882199e09b7e9e6989a68d6ea2495d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F04%2F112638_11882199e09b7e9e6989a68d6ea2495d.png&h=ab9c39be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<em><div style=\"text-align: center;\">攞到飛嗰下真係幾興奮</div></em><br />\n<br />\n好方便，有好多賣飛嘅網站<br />\n可以睇多幾個格下價<br />\n賣飛網站 eg<br />\n1. <a href=\"https://www.brazilbookers.com/brazil-carnival/rio-carnival-tickets/book-your-rio-tickets.asp#tit_allocated\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.brazilbookers.com%2Fbrazil-carnival%2Frio-carnival-tickets%2Fbook-your-rio-tickets.asp%23tit_allocated&d=aJy3RA7fpCa2KE6CQkcak5ggdM0W6%2BkgeusliPwa7Y4%3D&h=87159fcc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.brazilbookers.com/brazil-carnival/rio-carnival-tickets/book-your-rio-tickets.asp#tit_allocated</a><br />\n（呢個網好正，解釋晒啲座位係點分）<br />\n2. <a href=\"https://rio-carnival.net/EN/Tickets\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Frio-carnival.net%2FEN%2FTickets&d=aJy3RA7fpCa2KE6CQkcak5ggdM0W6%2BkgeusliPwa7Y4%3D&h=f79755f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://rio-carnival.net/EN/Tickets</a><br />\n3. <a href=\"https://www.carnivalbookers.com/rio-brazil/carnival/tickets/2019/outlet\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.carnivalbookers.com%2Frio-brazil%2Fcarnival%2Ftickets%2F2019%2Foutlet&d=aJy3RA7fpCa2KE6CQkcak5ggdM0W6%2BkgeusliPwa7Y4%3D&h=ccb3b8ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.carnivalbookers.com/rio-brazil/carnival/tickets/2019/outlet</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有咩位揀？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要首先係分區，有1-12區<br />\nparade由1區行到第12區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">第9區係遊客區</span>，除左呢區有劃位之外，其他區都係亂咁坐/企<br />\n呢區應該係比較安全，聽講啲staff又會識英文，所以啲飛係比較貴。<br />\n我就係坐呢區嘅Grandstand，60蚊美金。而第二區嘅同樣座位，只係要30-40美金。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過我都好後悔俾多呢廿蚊。<br />\n首先，其實成個會場都係好安全，有好多保安/工作人員，冇乜閒雜人可以入到個場，所以我唔覺得第九區同其他區有咩分別。<br />\n其次，其實啲staff都係唔多識英文，加上你黎睇show，又唔係黎搵人談心，所以都係算吧啦<br />\n仲有，其實開左Show，都冇人會理你張飛係坐邊，個個high起上黎都係亂咁黎。<br />\n<br />\n所以，都係慳番甘蚊啦。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/04/112710_8da04f1f7d14e7e2061234ed509fe198.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F04%2F112710_8da04f1f7d14e7e2061234ed509fe198.png&h=f5cabd36&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/04/112715_82ab1a7e7ac35002d17bdb9a53be5a5d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F04%2F112715_82ab1a7e7ac35002d17bdb9a53be5a5d.png&h=b5b7bc10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<em><div style=\"text-align: center;\">守衛深嚴</div></em><br />\n<br />\n另外，就係分前後，主要平啲嘅<br />\n一係就坐Grandstand<br />\n一係就坐Front box<br />\n<br />\n前者遠啲，不過啲梯級好分明，前面冇咁易遮到你。後者就好近啲表演者，但個斜度冇咁分明，有機會俾前面遮到你。<br />\n<br />\n我嘅意見係，想影大頭靚相嘅朋友就坐Frontbox，想宏觀啲睇成個show嘅朋友就坐Grandstand啦。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/04/112328_9012be9c2fe651460befb5b80ab73099.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F04%2F112328_9012be9c2fe651460befb5b80ab73099.png&h=4cec0e82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n自己睇下咩位啱你啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.brazilbookers.com/brazil-carnival/rio-carnival-tickets/book-your-rio-tickets.asp#tit_allocated\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.brazilbookers.com%2Fbrazil-carnival%2Frio-carnival-tickets%2Fbook-your-rio-tickets.asp%23tit_allocated&d=aJy3RA7fpCa2KE6CQkcak5ggdM0W6%2BkgeusliPwa7Y4%3D&h=87159fcc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.brazilbookers.com/brazil-carnival/rio-carnival-tickets/book-your-rio-tickets.asp#tit_allocated</a>"},{"pid":"91139da084791e5a4b9f369c933b8ed362d401d0","tid":1047273,"uid":231598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T00:21:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">廢話少講<br />\n睇相睇片啦</span></span><br />\n由於我睇嗰日係超大雨<br />\n所以都影唔到咩靚相<br />\n係咁2睇下啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/04/113334_bf52139f3695947b55d4ee3c73abe3a9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F04%2F113334_bf52139f3695947b55d4ee3c73abe3a9.png&h=94b13f19&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/04/113339_2d54afbd9aa32c75e6cfa72e5b85bc60.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F04%2F113339_2d54afbd9aa32c75e6cfa72e5b85bc60.png&h=f35073b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<em><div style=\"text-align: center;\">比賽期間係會封路</div></em><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/04/113533_db9691f2eecd0f0c7336112890100952.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F04%2F113533_db9691f2eecd0f0c7336112890100952.png&h=fdf58153&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/04/113539_f43c8b8ae1e37e43c0335b9b47d0d289.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F04%2F113539_f43c8b8ae1e37e43c0335b9b47d0d289.png&h=29ccefeb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/04/113545_a9f862d0392299854cd44819a3f7cc80.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F04%2F113545_a9f862d0392299854cd44819a3f7cc80.png&h=04fe98f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<em><div style=\"text-align: center;\">場內有野食賣<br />\n都唔算太貴<br />\n我呢set 50hkd</div></em><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/04/113722_e03c325b38299dbda497d46c0b9f2e9e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F04%2F113722_e03c325b38299dbda497d46c0b9f2e9e.png&h=6378fd87&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/04/113728_135b44dd20038363777f67c0946a34c5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F04%2F113728_135b44dd20038363777f67c0946a34c5.png&h=3fe92908&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/04/113738_44f2023864e8c6c1723e967251696722.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F04%2F113738_44f2023864e8c6c1723e967251696722.png&h=70c65748&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<em><div style=\"text-align: center;\">我睇嗰日係超大雨<br />\n條街都水浸<br />\n本身九點開始，但大雨到十一點幾先夾硬開始<br />\n個個都濕住身咁睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></em><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n終於開始嚕<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/05/080108_ae094e4549801e711817d09c5fb84a12.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F05%2F080108_ae094e4549801e711817d09c5fb84a12.png&h=cb6aa174&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/05/080123_0e231cb3e71b2a47280d09bf45887814.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F05%2F080123_0e231cb3e71b2a47280d09bf45887814.png&h=7701f6a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<em><div style=\"text-align: center;\">點解啲花車可以整到咁靚<br />\n初級組已經咁嘅級數</div></em>"},{"pid":"b85d6540643c830acb98f24aae632ff6ace690c4","tid":1047273,"uid":231598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T02:51:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/05/080203_a7ba3bc055598ea89dcea2feda4dd0e1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F05%2F080203_a7ba3bc055598ea89dcea2feda4dd0e1.png&h=f29bdc18&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/05/080218_8b4ec3edc4a6d2ecbddf135812ec6960.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F05%2F080218_8b4ec3edc4a6d2ecbddf135812ec6960.png&h=95897bb9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<em><div style=\"text-align: center;\">唔好Zoom咁大</div></em>"},{"pid":"eb893133099ce9062b133d64e8a7f9bf75d3661e","tid":1047273,"uid":231598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T11:28:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/05/080314_8b00c370a5193cb7693296e4af2c9db7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F05%2F080314_8b00c370a5193cb7693296e4af2c9db7.png&h=e3bdb1f1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/05/080327_8dcf851d84b329ee6036045b5000b51e.pn